he knows has changed his life.

51:45.033 --> 51:48.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JERRY BRUCE HENNON: The
transplant, I feel like that's
the greatest and worst possible

51:49.300 --> 51:51.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
